data.description: Why rent when you can own for less? Don't miss out on this move in ready home in the heart of La Farge! Enjoy small town living with lower taxes in this adorable one bedroom, one bath home. The eat in kitchen features plenty of storage and opens to the large living room with area for an additional dining space. Enjoy the large bedroom (that could be split into two bedrooms if desired) with plenty of space for extra living & storage. The front entry has been turned into a little nursery that could could be used as a reading nook or huge closet! Explore the expansive backyard with an oversized deck and a large patio with a fire pit. The home also has a great sized yard for kids to play. This move in ready home also has new insulation added in the basement, newer windows and a newer furnace.
